 If the concern is not resolved, the employee may escalate the matter to the HR Business Partner and subsequently to the HR Head for final resolution\n3. All escalations must be made in writing with supporting documentation\n\n**Review and Amendment of the Payroll Policy**\n\nThe Payroll Policy will be reviewed annually or as necessitated by changes in applicable tax laws, labour regulations, statutory requirements, or organisational restructuring. Any amendments to this policy will be agreed to and employees are encouraged to contact the HR Division or designated payroll helpdesk for any clarifications regarding this policy.	2026-04-10 10:07:09.267257
