. |\n\n**Key Differences:**\n\n* Bereavement leave is a separate policy with a specific duration.\n* Termination policies differ between cause and without cause termination.\n* Resignation policies differ from termination policies.\n* Policy revision is an annual process to update policies with changing legislation and employment trends.\n\nSources:\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf	2026-04-13 14:30:48.278848
