um leave duration for long-term illness\n* 1,250 hours: minimum hours required within 12 months for long-term illness eligibility\n* 2 months: maximum bereavement leave extension\n* 3 consecutive days: minimum notice required for resignation\n* 2 weeks: minimum notice required for resignation (for most employees)\n* 1 month: minimum notice required for resignation (for highly specialized or executive positions)	2026-04-10 12:50:14.221757
