ve different rules for overtime pay. |\n\n**Key Differences:**\n\n* Leave Policy has more types of leave and more flexible leave request rules.\n* Payroll Policy has a different pay structure and rules for overtime pay.\n* Leave Policy and Payroll Policy have different accrual rates and rules for leave.\n\nSources:\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf	2026-04-13 16:06:12.991182
