3f3a2fb6-6005-4a8d-bdfd-a8588fddf314	fb52dfd8-ade8-4e45-b9b9-b817d8e006fc	2	summarise the recruitment policy at artemis	**Recruitment Policy at Artemis**\n\n**Summary**\n\nThe Recruitment Policy at Artemis Technologies Pvt. Ltd. defines the standardized procedures for attracting, evaluating, and hiring qualified candidates. The policy aims to ensure a fair, transparent, and efficient hiring process, aligned with the organization's strategic goals and values.\n\n**Key Points:**\n\n* **Objectives:**\n\t+ Recruit highly qualified and competent individuals\n\t+ Ensure a fair, unbiased, and transparent hiring process\n\t+ Promote diversity and inclusion within the organization\n\t+ Maintain consistency and efficiency in recruitment practices\n\t+ Align hiring decisions with organizational goals\n* **Scope:**\n\t+ Applies to all recruitment activities within Artemis Technologies Pvt. Ltd.\n\t+ Covers all stages of recruitment from job requirement identification to onboarding\n* **Job Requirement Identification:**\n\t+ Hiring manager and HR team responsible for defining job role and responsibilities\n\t+ Identifying required technical and soft skills\n\t+ Determining experience level and qualifications\n\t+ Preparing a detailed job description\n* **Equal Opportunity Policy:**\n\t+ Artemis Technologies Pvt. Ltd. is committed to providing equal employment opportunities to all candidates\n\t+ Prohibits discrimination based on gender, race, religion, nationality, disability, or background\n* **Confidentiality:**\n\t+ All recruitment-related information must be handled with strict confidentiality\n\t+ Candidate data must be securely stored and protected\n\n**Policy Documents:**\n\n* Document: artemis_recruitment_policy (1).pdf\n* Document: artemis_employee_handbook.pdf (for general information on the company culture and values)\n\nSources:\n- artemis_recruitment_policy (1).pdf\n- ArtemisDisciplinaryPolicy (2).pdf\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf\n- Artemis_IT_Security_Policy (1).pdf\n- Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf	2026-04-14 09:47:19.678659
