mployee_Handbook.pdf provides more detailed information on paid time off, sick leave, and parental leave, while Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf focuses on attendance, leave, and loss of pay.\n* Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf provides more detailed information on leave encashment, gratuity, and termination procedures.\n* Artemis_Employee_Handbook.pdf emphasizes the importance of pre-approval for leave and reimbursement, while Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf requires pre-approval for reimbursement and has a specific time limit for submitting claims.\n\nSources:\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf\n- Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf	2026-04-14 10:08:38.830478
