ec865925-8d40-446b-b811-923d037b2af6	ca15452f-c7e2-4d0c-b078-0c2a08efeb71	1	compare paid and unpaid leaves	**Comparison of Paid and Unpaid Leaves**\n\n**Policy Documents:** artemis_employee_handbook.pdf and Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf\n\n**Paid Leaves:**\n\n| **Leave Type** | **Employee Handbook** | **Payroll Policy** |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Paid Time Off (PTO) | Not specified | Not applicable |\n| Sick Leave | 1 week of paid sick leave | 1 week of paid sick leave |\n| Jury Duty Leave | Paid jury duty leave | Not specified |\n| Parental Leave | Paternity and maternity leave | Not specified |\n| Bereavement Leave | 1 day of bereavement leave | Not specified |\n| Holiday Pay | Exempt employees: normal compensation, Permanent non-exempt employees: holiday pay after 3 months | Not specified |\n\n**Unpaid Leaves:**\n\n| **Leave Type** | **Employee Handbook** | **Payroll Policy** |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Unpaid Time Off | Floating day, observe a religious holiday, or use PTO | Not specified |\n| Unpaid Leave Extension | Up to 2 months | Not specified |\n| Jury Duty Leave | Not specified | Not applicable |\n| Bereavement Leave | Not specified | Not applicable |\n\n**Similarities:**\n\n* Both policies offer paid sick leave (1 week).\n* Both policies mention jury duty leave, but the employee handbook specifies that it is paid, while the payroll policy does not.\n* Both policies mention bereavement leave, but the employee handbook specifies that it is 1 day, while the payroll policy does not.\n\n**Differences:**\n\n* The employee handbook offers a floating day, while the payroll policy does not.\n* The employee handbook offers an unpaid leave extension of up to 2 months, while the payroll policy does not.\n* The employee handbook specifies that exempt employees receive normal compensation for holidays, while the payroll policy does not mention holiday pay.\n* The employee handbook mentions parental leave, while the payroll policy does not.\n* The employee handbook specifies that bereavement leave is 1 day, while the payroll policy does not mention bereavement leave.\n\nSources:\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf\n- Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf	2026-04-14 10:43:38.208704
