5ce340b0-e9a7-4437-844d-a15acf9e9f6e	5cc9ad7c-a73c-46b8-a2ac-49c57117ec74	document_summarization	{"query": "what are the benefits at artemis?", "user_role": "employee", "selected_tool": "document_summarization"}	{"sources": [{"category": "leave", "file_name": "artemis_employee_handbook.pdf", "page_number": null}, {"category": "payroll", "file_name": "Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf", "page_number": null}], "summary": "**Summary of Benefits at Artemis**\\n\\nBased on the Artemis Payroll Policy and Employee Handbook, the benefits at Artemis include:\\n\\n**Eligible Employees:**\\n- All full-time and part-time employees of Artemis Technology Limited\\n- Contract employees and consultants remunerated through the Company's payroll system\\n- Interns and trainees receiving stipends under Artemis supervision\\n\\n**Benefits Components:**\\n\\n* **Gross Salary Components:**\\n + Basic Salary (fully taxable)\\n + House Rent Allowance (partially exempt)\\n + Special Allowance (fully taxable)\\n + Performance Bonus (fully taxable)\\n + Leave Travel Allowance (exempt, subject to conditions)\\n + Medical Allowance (exempt)\\n* **Other Benefits:**\\n + Overtime pay\\n + Reimbursements\\n + Advances\\n + Final settlements\\n\\n**Key Principles:**\\n- Accuracy and timeliness in payroll processing\\n- Confidentiality in payroll matters\\n\\n**Source Documents:**\\n- Artemis Payroll Policy (HR-PP-002)\\n- Artemis Employee Handbook\\n\\n**Effective Date:** April 2025\\n\\n**Note:** The benefits and policies outlined in this summary are subject to change and may not be comprehensive. It is recommended to refer to the original source documents for the most up-to-date information.", "chunks_used": 10, "summary_type": "concise"}	2026-04-10 15:02:15.720132
