6b55e648-a679-485f-a9d9-0e9767a9e3e2	0654d35e-d48f-4895-9c53-57c8d2cd84d9	policy_retrieval_tool	{"query": "tell me about the leave policy", "top_k": 5, "user_role": "Employee"}	{"answer": "Based on the provided policy excerpts, here are the relevant rules regarding leave policy:\\n\\n* If you are absent for more than three days of sick leave, you must complete a sick leave form for insurance purposes. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If you are a new mother or father, you must give at least three months' notice before your leave begins. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* Depending on local or national law, pregnant women can take part of their leave before labor. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If you suffer complications during childbirth or have other issues, you can ask for leave. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If national law stipulates longer leave, the company will follow the law. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)", "chunks_count": 5, "sources_count": 5}	2026-04-16 10:31:23.292205
283d4778-2f7c-4e02-97a9-ad7e34527a9d	fa9b4cd2-9883-403d-9a37-b62717f0dce8	policy_retrieval_tool	{"query": "what is leave policy", "top_k": 5, "user_role": "Employee"}	{"answer": "Based on the provided policy excerpts, here are the relevant leave policies:\\n\\n* Sick leave: \\n  - You may be required to complete a sick leave form for insurance purposes if you are absent for more than three days of sick leave. (Document: artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n  - The exact process for reporting sick leave is not specified in the provided excerpts.\\n\\nNote: The policy documents do not cover other types of leave, such as vacation or family leave.", "chunks_count": 5, "sources_count": 5}	2026-04-14 04:17:12.236779
