c4b02f13-2e9b-45f0-bda5-5c257c8578bb	bdd02ecd-e643-4a14-95ab-316eca0f0644	policy_retrieval_tool	{"query": "tell me about the leave policy", "top_k": 5, "user_role": "Employee"}	{"answer": "Based on the provided policy excerpts, here are the relevant rules regarding leave policy:\\n\\n* If you are absent for more than three days of sick leave, you will need to complete a sick leave form for insurance purposes. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If you are a new mother or father, you should give at least three months' notice before your leave begins. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* Depending on local or national law, pregnant women can take part of their leave before labor. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If you suffer complications during childbirth or have other issues, you can ask for leave. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)\\n* If national law stipulates longer leave, the company will follow the law. (artemis_employee_handbook.pdf, Page: None)", "chunks_count": 5, "sources_count": 5}	2026-04-16 11:17:08.72046
d8b48f90-ebae-43be-bd90-b7186213c4e5	bdd02ecd-e643-4a14-95ab-316eca0f0644	policy_retrieval_tool	{"query": "what is the paid time off policy", "top_k": 5, "user_role": "Employee"}	{"answer": "Based on the provided policy excerpts from the artemis_employee_handbook.pdf document, the Paid Time Off (PTO) policy is as follows:\\n\\n* Employees receive 20 days of PTO per year.\\n* PTO accrual begins the day you join the company and you receive 1.7 days per month.\\n* You can take your PTO at any time after your first week with the company and you can use time off you haven't accrued yet.\\n* You will earn one additional day per year after your first year with the company, with a cap at 25 days overall.\\n* If you want to use PTO, send a request through our HRIS. If your manager or HR approves, you are permitted to take your leave.\\n* You do not have to specify a reason for requesting PTO.\\n* You can transfer any remaining PTO to the next year.\\n* We encourage you to use your time off throughout the year.", "chunks_count": 5, "sources_count": 5}	2026-04-16 12:04:49.916509
