4fc809bb-6a8e-455c-b7d5-34ccbe72c86a	a43f2bcc-78f3-41c0-8169-3bc49031bc7e	comparison_tool	{"query": "compare between payroll and leave policy", "user_role": "HR"}	{"answer": "**Comparison between Payroll and Leave Policy**\\n\\n**Policy Documents:**\\n- Artemis_Payroll_Policy (1).pdf\\n- artemis_employee_handbook.pdf\\n\\n**Comparison Table:**\\n\\n| **Category** | **Payroll Policy** | **Leave Policy** | **Similarities** | **Differences** |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n| **Salary Disbursement** | Monthly by bank transfers | Not mentioned |  |  |\\n| **Attendance Tracking** | Integrated with HRMS | Not mentioned |  |  |\\n| **Leave Encashment** | Encashment of unused EL balance | Not mentioned |  |  |\\n| **Gratuity** | Payable upon completion of 5 years | Not mentioned |  |  |\\n| **Record Keeping** | Monthly Payroll Register: Duration of employment + 8 years | Not mentioned |  |  |\\n| **Policy Review** | Annual or as necessitated by changes | Annual revision to bring it up to date with legislation and employment trends |  |  |\\n| **Related Policies** | Compensation & Benefits Policy, Leave Policy, Expense Reimbursement & Travel Policy, Separation & Exit Policy, Data Privacy & Confidentiality Policy, IT & Acceptable Use Policy, Disciplinary Policy (HR-DP-001), Whistleblower Policy | Employee Handbook, Compensation & Benefits Policy, Leave Policy, Expense Reimbursement & Travel Policy, Separation & Exit Policy, Data Privacy & Confidentiality Policy |  |  |\\n\\n**Similarities:**\\n\\n- Both policies are reviewed annually or as necessitated by changes.\\n- Both policies are related to other company policies.\\n\\n**Differences:**\\n\\n- Salary disbursement is mentioned in the Payroll Policy but not in the Leave Policy.\\n- Attendance tracking is integrated with HRMS in the Payroll Policy but not mentioned in the Leave Policy.\\n- Leave encashment is mentioned in the Payroll Policy but not in the Leave Policy.\\n- Gratuity is payable upon completion of 5 years in the Payroll Policy but not mentioned in the Leave Policy.\\n- Record keeping is mentioned in the Payroll Policy but not in the Leave Policy.\\n- Related policies are mentioned in both documents but with some differences.", "chunks_count": 20, "sources_count": 2}	2026-04-16 06:53:51.53775
