788f370a-0222-488d-be29-f6bc49e3d21d	43599a4a-e7e2-49fe-85e7-f610998bb594	10	• Document title and unique reference number or code \n• Date of creation or last revision \n• Name and designation of the author or responsible officer \n• Classification level (as per Section 6) \n• Version number for documents subject to revision \n5.2 Filing & Storage \nRecords must be filed systematically within 24 hours of creation or receipt. The following rules \napply: \n• Physical documents must be stored in designated, labeled filing cabinets or archives \nwithin each department \n• Electronic documents must be saved in the authorized document management system \n(DMS) under the correct folder hierarchy \n• Documents must not be stored exclusively on personal devices, personal cloud \naccounts, or email inboxes	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
