851b43cd-2ecd-44e5-af67-3f95895b6fc8	43599a4a-e7e2-49fe-85e7-f610998bb594	20	RECORDS MANAGEMENT & ADMINISTRATION POLICY   |   Artemis | Human Resources \n& Administration Division \nPolicy Code: HR-ADP-003   |   Version: 1.0   |   Effective Date: April 2025   |   Page 6 \nRecord Category Specific Record Type Retention Period \nHR Records Separation & exit documentation Duration of employment \n+ 5 years \nFinancial Records Invoices, receipts & expense \nclaims \n8 years from financial \nyear end \nFinancial Records Payroll records & salary slips 8 years from financial \nyear end \nFinancial Records Tax filings & statutory records 8 years from financial \nyear end \nLegal & Compliance Corporate registration & licenses Permanent \nLegal & Compliance Contracts & agreements Term of contract + 7 \nyears \nLegal & Compliance Board minutes & resolutions Permanent	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
