bce6fa40-9b82-4a79-b9d7-a931365374d0	43599a4a-e7e2-49fe-85e7-f610998bb594	27	RECORDS MANAGEMENT & ADMINISTRATION POLICY   |   Artemis | Human Resources \n& Administration Division \nPolicy Code: HR-ADP-003   |   Version: 1.0   |   Effective Date: April 2025   |   Page 8 \nThis Records Management & Administration Policy will be reviewed annually or upon any \nsignificant change to Artemis's operational structure, legal obligations, or document \nmanagement systems. Amendments will be communicated to all employees through official HR \nand Administration channels, and updated acknowledgment will be required from relevant staff \nwithin 30 days of release. \n13. RELATED POLICIES \nThis policy must be read in conjunction with the following Artemis policies: \n• Employee Handbook \n• Disciplinary Policy (HR-DP-001) \n• IT & Information Security Policy (HR-ISP-002)	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
