2cf49fd9-8f1a-42fb-aecf-85ab8cb237cc	694562db-9c80-4fc6-9252-e6c3df7a6a7c	4	All users are individually accountable for their actions on Artemis systems. Activity logs are \nmaintained and may be audited. \n3.6 Compliance \nArtemis will maintain compliance with all applicable data protection laws, industry standards, \nand regulatory requirements including but not limited to GDPR, IT Act 2000 (India), and ISO/IEC \n27001 standards. \n4. ACCEPTABLE USE OF IT RESOURCES \n4.1 Permitted Use \nArtemis IT resources are provided primarily for business purposes. Incidental and reasonable \npersonal use is permitted provided it does not: \n• Interfere with the performance of professional duties \n• Consume significant bandwidth or storage resources \n• Violate any provision of this policy or applicable law \n• Compromise system security or data integrity \n4.2 Prohibited Use	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
