b9ead57f-159d-48e4-bc15-94e8cf4b4cef	acd48414-5eb1-4c91-9479-3e34b77f48fb	0	Artemis Technologies Pvt. Ltd. - Recruitment Policy \n1. Introduction \nThis Recruitment Policy defines the standardized procedures followed by Artemis Technologies \nPvt. Ltd. to attract, evaluate, and hire qualified candidates. The objective is to ensure that all \nrecruitment activities are conducted in a fair, transparent, and efficient manner, aligned with the \norganization’s strategic goals and values. \n2. Objectives \nThe key objectives of this policy are: \n To recruit highly qualified and competent individuals  \n To ensure a fair, unbiased, and transparent hiring process  \n To promote diversity and inclusion within the organization  \n To maintain consistency and efficiency in recruitment practices  \n To align hiring decisions with organizational goals  \n3. Scope	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
bcc72854-5606-44e4-af59-fd190c4a48cc	acd48414-5eb1-4c91-9479-3e34b77f48fb	1	 To maintain consistency and efficiency in recruitment practices  \n To align hiring decisions with organizational goals  \n3. Scope \nThis policy applies to all recruitment activities within Artemis Technologies Pvt. Ltd., including: \n Human Resources (HR) team  \n Hiring managers  \n Interview panel members  \nIt covers all stages of recruitment from job requirement identification to onboarding. \n4. Job Requirement Identification \nThe recruitment process begins with identifying the need for hiring. The hiring manager, in \ncoordination with the HR team, is responsible for: \n Defining the job role and responsibilities  \n Identifying required technical and soft skills  \n Determining experience level and qualifications  \n Preparing a detailed job description	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
5823d30c-6383-41e3-bf3b-c14726c85c32	acd48414-5eb1-4c91-9479-3e34b77f48fb	2	 Identifying required technical and soft skills  \n Determining experience level and qualifications  \n Preparing a detailed job description  \n Justifying the hiring requirement  \n5. Job Posting and Sourcing \nOnce the job requirements are finalized, the position is advertised through appropriate channels:	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
5fcf69b2-fe98-43b2-84b4-8d781821adf7	acd48414-5eb1-4c91-9479-3e34b77f48fb	3	 Internal job postings within the organization  \n External job portals (e.g., LinkedIn, job boards)  \n Employee referral programs  \n Campus recruitment initiatives  \nThe objective is to attract a diverse and qualified pool of candidates. \n6. Application Screening \nAll received applications are reviewed by the HR team. Candidates are shortlisted based on: \n Educational qualifications  \n Relevant skills and experience  \n Alignment with job requirements  \n Resume quality and completeness  \nOnly candidates meeting the criteria are progressed to the next stage. \n7. Selection Process \nThe selection process is designed to assess candidates comprehensively and consists of the \nfollowing stages: \n7.1 Technical Evaluation	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
82ce4d0f-fa9a-429c-b09a-494a0b45886e	acd48414-5eb1-4c91-9479-3e34b77f48fb	4	The selection process is designed to assess candidates comprehensively and consists of the \nfollowing stages: \n7.1 Technical Evaluation \n Conducted through coding tests, case studies, or role-specific assessments  \n Evaluates technical knowledge and problem-solving ability  \n7.2 HR Interview \n Assesses communication skills, attitude, and cultural fit  \n Evaluates candidate expectations and career goals  \n7.3 Final Interview \n Conducted by the hiring manager or senior leadership  \n Focuses on decision-making ability, role suitability, and alignment with company \nobjectives  \n8. Offer and Onboarding \nCandidates who successfully clear all selection stages are provided with an offer letter that \nincludes: \n Job title and responsibilities	\N	2026-04-10 09:48:05.090797
